chemaxon.marvin.view

Class ViewParameterConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • chemaxon.marvin.common.ParameterConstants
      • chemaxon.marvin.view.ViewParameterConstants

  • public class ViewParameterConstants
extends ParameterConstants
    Parameters of MarvinView Applet and Bean.
    The parameters of the JMView applet can be set using the <param> HTML tag. The parameters of the MViewPane JavaBean component can be set using the setParams method.
    Since:
    Marvin 5.2
    Version:
    5.2.2, 05/06/2009
    Author:
    Eva Hollo, Judit Vasko-Szedlar
